Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.24,0:00:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,the willingness to let it all go and go\Nback up like a cork in the water.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.16,0:00:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Anybody got any other ideas? Why does\Nsome people have to hit such a
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,incredibly horrible bottom before they\Nlet go? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.32,0:00:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,>> My thought on that is that\Nmy perception is your body
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.19,0:00:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,feel\Nwhat what is horrible to me is horrible
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,to someone else and so I can only deal\Nwith my body I can't deal with I'm not
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.23,0:00:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,coming\N>> I believe that is so also some people
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.76,0:00:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,have the capacity to to experience and\Nsurvive suffering of amazing degrees
