Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.00,0:01:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,>> big deal to them in your reality as\Nsomebody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.15,0:01:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,>> That's correct. And each person has\Ntheir own threshold. And I suppose you
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.79,0:01:25.92,Default,,0,0,0,,don't forget don't forget spiritual\Ntraining. A lot of spiritual trainings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.92,0:01:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,are very severe. I've been through some\Nthat were, you know, about as far as you
