Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.79,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Made s seem like a playground. It was\Npretty severe. But even, you know, was
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the bottom for some people. You remember\Nthose of you who did EST, the fact you
