Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:02:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,shock that they couldn't look at their\Nwatch or
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.00,0:02:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,uh not going to the bathroom. That was\Nthe big one. And then
