Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.36,0:02:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody's stuff came up. You know,\Nlike you were saying, there's a great
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.23,0:02:26.56,Default,,0,0,0,,variety. Some of which to the observer\Nwe would think is ridiculous, but to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.56,0:02:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,them it was really a crisis. I suppose\Nif you've been beaten up at age 3
