Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.44,0:02:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we all create our own bottom by either\Nconscious or unconscious decisions.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And many decisions as you do spiritual\Nwork you become conscious of that you
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.68,0:03:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,made them but you' forgotten them or\Nthey're unconscious that you obviously
