Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.04,0:03:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,>> When I was unconscious,\N>> right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.79,0:03:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,>> And and my picture would be that my ego\Ncollaborated with my body in that might
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.23,0:03:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,create addictive behaviors that are with\Nthe mind or the body itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.95,0:03:59.28,Default,,0,0,0,,>> Um so it's collaboration evil in the\Nbody and for the spirit to break through
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.28,0:04:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,that you know one first has to be\Nconscious awake and then you realize
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe how much ground you lost. So you\Nknow the earlier you can become
