Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.63,0:04:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you know bottom I'm like five inches\Nfrom bottom I had no idea
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.08,0:04:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,>> it is a very good question because you\Ndo wonder why people say other people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,have sort of congenital capacity to\Nhandle greater pain people have a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,higher higher and lower pain thresholds\Nwhich you can test out and some people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.72,0:04:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,have very low pain thresholds.\NUm experientially I can tolerate things
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.24,0:04:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,that are excruciating beyond probably\N95% of the population capacity and
