Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,uh, flinch because you've been trained\Nto do that. All right. So,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,we'd say there's been probably some\Nagreements made to which you are
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.44,0:05:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,unaware. So, the best thing would be to\Npresume that you made that choice and
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.36,0:05:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that you made that agreement. Shall we\Nsee
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.44,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be wise operationally it's\Nbest to presume that that is a choice
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.56,0:05:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and a decision that you made is it\Noperationally just the fact that you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,can't consciously recall it doesn't mean\Nanything. Anybody's been in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,psychoanalysis knows that you made a lot\Nof decisions that were totally
