Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.40,0:26:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond 600, you're not very useful. You\Nyou're not used useful in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.00,0:27:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Beyond 590, you're not very useful in\Nthe world. You can sit there and bless
